Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:32.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，你回来了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嘿，史蒂仔\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hey, Steve-O.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们对之前的事非常抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs32}We're so sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:37.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}别管这些了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们必须追上她！\N{\fnArial\fs32}We have to catch up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:39.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:40.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}谁？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:41.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}蓝钻石\N{\fnArial\fs32}Blue Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}蓝钻石？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Blue Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:45.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}噢，哦，不，在地球？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, oh, on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:47.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我的天！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Holy smokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她们总算要现身了\N{\fnArial\fs32}They're all coming out of the woodwork.
