Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:51.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我-我得坐下来\N{\fnArial\fs32}I-I need to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:53.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她带走了爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}She took Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:56.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她像外星人一样绑架了他，而这都是我的错！\N{\fnArial\fs32}She alien abducted him, and it's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她抓走了格雷格？\N{\fnArial\fs32}She took Greg?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:59.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们的格雷格？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Our Greg?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}难道还有别的格雷格？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What other Greg is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:02.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们该怎么将他带回来？\N{\fnArial\fs32}How are we gonna get him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:04.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她甚至要他有什么用？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What does she even want him for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:07.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}吃掉他？将他放进动物园？\N{\fnArial\fs32}To eat him? To put him in a zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:08.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}等等\N{\fnArial\fs32}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:10.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还真可能是这样\N{\fnArial\fs32}That might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:12.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她会吃了他？！\N{\fnArial\fs32}She's gonna eat him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}什么？不！\N{\fnArial\fs32}What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:16.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但确实有个-不，不，\N{\fnArial\fs32}But there was a -- No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:18.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但不可能仍然还在\N{\fnArial\fs32}It couldn't possibly still exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:19.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}至少从我们-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Not since we --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:20.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:22.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}粉钻石隐秘的人类动物园\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pink Diamond's insidious human zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:23.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}当她还在地球时，\N{\fnArial\fs32}During her reign on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:28.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}粉钻石将人类从他们的家人旁掠走\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pink Diamond stole humans from their families
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}作为她征程的一个奖杯\N{\fnArial\fs32}as trophies of her conquests.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:31.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你一定是在开玩笑吧？\N{\fnArial\fs32}You got to be kidding. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:32.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，不\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:33.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这是真的\N{\fnArial\fs32}It was very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:36.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}当我还在服务于...母世界\N{\fnArial\fs32}When I still served... Homeworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:37.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我亲眼看到的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I saw it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:40.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一个深空中的私人野生动物园\N{\fnArial\fs32}A private menagerie deep in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}人类被困在其中\N{\fnArial\fs32}Humans in captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:43.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们一直没能救他们出来\N{\fnArial\fs32}We were never able to rescue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:46.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}战争开始后我们一直没有能力接近他们\N{\fnArial\fs32}We had no way to get to them after the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:49.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但这是五千年前了\N{\fnArial\fs32}But that was over 5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你真的确定格雷格在那里？\N{\fnArial\fs32}You really think Greg's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，蓝钻石想让他活着？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, Blue Diamond wanted him alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:56.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对，是的！她很喜欢他！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yes, yes! She liked him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我想不出还有什么地方她会安置他\N{\fnArial\fs32}I can't think of anywhere else she'd put him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:01:59.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果她想留着他，\N{\fnArial\fs32}if she wanted to keep him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果动物园还在的话，\N{\fnArial\fs32}That is if the zoo's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:03.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}只能去那里试试了\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:06.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但我们该怎么到那里？\N{\fnArial\fs32}But how are we going to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}用the Roaming Eye\N{\fnArial\fs32}With the Roaming Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:09.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}红宝石的太空船？\N{\fnArial\fs32}The Ruby ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:10.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:12.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们要前往太空了，\N{\fnArial\fs32}We're going into space,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而且我们一定要带回格雷格\N{\fnArial\fs32}and we're not coming back without Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:17.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们看看\N{\fnArial\fs32}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:20.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们的中子星定位器仍然在定位\N{\fnArial\fs32}Your pulsar trackers are tracking pulsars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:22.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}大气防护层看起来还能工作\N{\fnArial\fs32}The atmosphere shield seems functional,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:25.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但你们在太空中用不到那个，显然\N{\fnArial\fs32}but you're not going to need that in space, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:27.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}确保这对史蒂文是安全的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Make sure it's safe for Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:28.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}他应该没问题，\N{\fnArial\fs32}He should be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:30.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但我认为我得更改\N{\fnArial\fs32}but I think I should go in and change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:31.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}红宝石们设定的系统偏好\N{\fnArial\fs32}the system preferences the Rubies set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:34.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你感觉绿光相比红光怎么样\N{\fnArial\fs32}How do you feel about green lights instead of red?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:35.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没时间搞这些了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}There's no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果能用的话，咱们赶紧干！\N{\fnArial\fs32}If it works, - let's just do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起，康妮，但我们等不及了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry, Connie, but we just can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸身陷困境\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad's in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而且我们得前往太空将他带回来\N{\fnArial\fs32}and we need to go into space to get him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没时间了\N{\fnArial\fs32}There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:46.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们现在就走\N{\fnArial\fs32}We're going right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:49.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一定要在我们离开后保护好沙滩市\N{\fnArial\fs32}Just protect Beach City for me while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那么，如果我输入坐标，\N{\fnArial\fs32}So, if I input the coordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:52.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}它就会直接带我们过去？\N{\fnArial\fs32}it will take us right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}实际上更复杂一些\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's a little more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这不是你们那种第一代的“轻型风筝”\N{\fnArial\fs32}These aren't your era one light kites.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们很可能会“扭曲现实”\N{\fnArial\fs32}You're gonna be pretty much bending reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果要用引力引擎的话\N{\fnArial\fs32}if you turn on the gravity engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}考虑到这个，我真的该\N{\fnArial\fs32}Come to think of it, I should really change
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一起更改红宝石对那个设置的偏好\N{\fnArial\fs32}the ruby preferences on that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}所以呢？那个设的是红色！\N{\fnArial\fs32}So what? So it's red!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}快啊，快点！我们得走了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Come on, come on! We got to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}先不管红宝石，它能飞起来吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Rubies aside, will it fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:12.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}简单来说，可以\N{\fnArial\fs32}Short answer, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那么，出发！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}青金石，橄榄石，留在这里\N{\fnArial\fs32}Lapis, Peridot, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们得保护沙滩市\N{\fnArial\fs32}You'll have to protect Beach City
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}以防我们离开时有事发生\N{\fnArial\fs32}if something happens while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们可以相信我们\N{\fnArial\fs32}You can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不要担心，爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs32}Don't worry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:34.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们已经在路上了\N{\fnArial\fs32}We're on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我真希望他能看到这样的风景\N{\fnArial\fs32}I hope he got to see some of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这里的风光足够填满\N{\fnArial\fs32}There's enough out here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:41.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一整个有关宇宙的相册了\N{\fnArial\fs32}for a whole album about the cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:44.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}太空涡流\N{\fnArial\fs32}Space turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}飞的不错嘛\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sweet moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:57.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}等等\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好吧，我们还要飞多远-\N{\fnArial\fs32}All right, how much further till we get to --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:03.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起，红宝石\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry, Rubies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们真的该对她们做点什么\N{\fnArial\fs32}We should really do something about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们能在回来的路上接她们\N{\fnArial\fs32}We can pick them up on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:14.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸是首要任务\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还有多久我们能到那里？\N{\fnArial\fs32}How much longer till we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:19.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，按现在的速度\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well, at our current speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:23.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们到达人类动物园应该在...\N{\fnArial\fs32}we should be reaching the human zoo in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}大约七十人类年之后\N{\fnArial\fs32}approximately 70 human years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}刚好赶上格雷格的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Just in time for Greg's 110th anniversary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:28.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}110大寿\N{\fnArial\fs32}of being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}珍珠，我爸的身体状况\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pearl, my dad's not healthy enough
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}坚持不了那么久\N{\fnArial\fs32}to live that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:37.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃...你觉得我们能把时间砍到69年吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh...do you think he'll be able to make it to 109?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们走之前\N{\fnArial\fs32}Before we left,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:40.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}橄榄石提到了引力引擎\N{\fnArial\fs32}Peridot did mention a gravity engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，对啊，她说那会“扭曲现实”\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, yeah. She said it bends reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}噢，我确定她是在夸大其词\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, I'm sure she was exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这很可能只是改变速度的定义\N{\fnArial\fs32}It probably just alters the definition of speed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}通过操纵时空来达成，\N{\fnArial\fs32}by manipulating space time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但这对有机物质会有什么影响？\N{\fnArial\fs32}but what effect will that have on organic matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这有可能会扁平化史蒂文的身体\N{\fnArial\fs32}It might flatten Steven's body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}将其变成由皮肤和骨骼组成的烙饼\N{\fnArial\fs32}into a pancake of skin and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}骨头很恶心\N{\fnArial\fs32}Bones are gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你卧室里可有骨头\N{\fnArial\fs32}You have bones in your bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:01.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那不一样\N{\fnArial\fs32}That's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那是我的骨头\N{\fnArial\fs32}Those are my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果变成烙饼能拯救我爸爸，\N{\fnArial\fs32}If being a pancake means saving my dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那么，端上酱汁吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}then bring on the syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:17.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文？你还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我很好\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我感觉我刚刚晕了过去\N{\fnArial\fs32}I think I just blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:27.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，你们还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Um, are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你说呢？\N{\fnArial\fs32}You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，不，有地方不对\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh,{\i1} no,{\i} we're{\i1} not{\i} okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，为什么你们看起来怪怪的？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, why do you guys look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:38.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}引力传送似乎对我们的身体有影响\N{\fnArial\fs32}The gravity warp seems to be affecting our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一定要告诉我这会有持久的效果\N{\fnArial\fs32}Please tell me this lasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们的身体是由光组成的，\N{\fnArial\fs32}Our bodies are made of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而通常光会制造出质量\N{\fnArial\fs32}and usually they form a mass
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:46.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这取决于周围的气压\N{\fnArial\fs32}dependent on the air pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:49.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}与引力状况\N{\fnArial\fs32}and the level of gravity in the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但我们身处的情况\N{\fnArial\fs32}But we're in a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不适用于一般的物理规则\N{\fnArial\fs32}where the normal laws of physics don't apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}谁在乎呢？反正很有趣\N{\fnArial\fs32}Who cares? It's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这怎么有趣了？！\N{\fnArial\fs32}In what way is this funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那么，你们不是故意这么做的？\N{\fnArial\fs32}So, you guys aren't doing this on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:03.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们不能通过变形变回去吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Can't you shapeshift back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}等等\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:08.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哈，快看，美洲狮崽\N{\fnArial\fs32}Huh, check it out. Puma cub.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:11.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}飞船似乎通过散发某种能量\N{\fnArial\fs32}The ship seems to be putting out some kind of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:12.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}让我们保持现在的尺寸\N{\fnArial\fs32}keeping us in this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，我知道该怎么做了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, I know the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:16.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs32}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}橄榄石说这艘船是按红宝石校准的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Peridot said the ship was calibrated for Rubies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这肯定让你们都变成了红宝石的大小\N{\fnArial\fs32}It must be making you all Ruby sized.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:27.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}啊！为什么她从不告诉我们任何事？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ugh! Why doesn't she ever tell us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这就是为什么我们不要听她的话\N{\fnArial\fs32}This is why we don't listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也许我能更改设置\N{\fnArial\fs32}Maybe I can change the settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:35.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不！\N{\fnArial\fs32}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不是\N{\fnArial\fs32}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:45.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这好像行不通\N{\fnArial\fs32}This isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}试试手动调节\N{\fnArial\fs32}Try adjusting it manually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}喔，呃，也许是这个？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Whoa. Um, maybe this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好吧，所以它是干这个的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Okay, so that does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也许是这个？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Maybe this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}啊！为什么要搞得这么复杂？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Aah! Why is this so complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嘿，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hey, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这开始变得有点怪了，即使对我也是\N{\fnArial\fs32}This is getting a little weird, even for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我好像发现关闭按钮了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I think I found the off switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}伙计们！我-我做什么了？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Guys! W-What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:46.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}紫晶？石榴？珍珠？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Amethyst? Garnet? Pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:47.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们在哪？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}发生什么了？你们碎了？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What happened? Are you cracked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}紫晶通常已经恢复了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Amethyst is usually back by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，不！那是动物园\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, no. That's the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，我们要直接跟动物园撞上了，\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, we're gonna smash right into it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果还不减速的话\N{\fnArial\fs32}if we don't slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}上啊，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs32}Come on, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:10.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你能做到的\N{\fnArial\fs32}You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:12.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这没什么\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}宝石人们没事的\N{\fnArial\fs32}The gems are gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她们不会出事的\N{\fnArial\fs32}They got to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸也不会出事的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad's gonna be fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}虽然现在看起来不是这样，\N{\fnArial\fs32}It doesn't seem like it right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但待会，我们会在一起欢笑的\N{\fnArial\fs32}but later, we're gonna laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}只要我能让太空船停下\N{\fnArial\fs32}If I could just stop the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:49.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}它不会停下的\N{\fnArial\fs32}It isn't going to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没法解决这个问题\N{\fnArial\fs32}There's no fixing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这都是我的错\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:55.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我太着急了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I rushed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:59.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我逼着大家做出愚蠢又错误的决定\N{\fnArial\fs32}I pushed us into making stupid mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}本不用这样的\N{\fnArial\fs32}It didn't have to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我本应听石榴的话\N{\fnArial\fs32}I didn't have to not listen to Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我不应去韩国\N{\fnArial\fs32}I didn't have to go to Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:09.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我不应让你被蓝钻石永远带走\N{\fnArial\fs32}I didn't have to get you taken away forever by Blue Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我-我不是出于自私\N{\fnArial\fs32}I-I wasn't trying to be selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:22.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我这次只是想搞清都发生了什么\N{\fnArial\fs32}I just wanted to know what was going on for myself for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:27.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但现在我失去了所有人\N{\fnArial\fs32}But now I lost everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:32.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:34.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我想我的爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I want my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我只想见到我爸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I just want my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们回来了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}之前去哪了？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我之前非常担心！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我想你试图恢复我们身体的举动\N{\fnArial\fs32}I think in your attempt to fix our bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也许意外的\N{\fnArial\fs32}you may have accidentally
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}关闭了所有的校准\N{\fnArial\fs32}shut off the calibration altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:11.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们由光组成的外形无法跟上\N{\fnArial\fs32}Our light-composed forms couldn't keep up with a ship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:13.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}超过光速移动的飞船\N{\fnArial\fs32}moving faster than the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:17.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}所以你们刚才只是一直落在飞船后方？\N{\fnArial\fs32}So you were just lagging behind the ship this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是啊，不要太担心\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah. Don't worry about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}紫晶很喜欢这样\N{\fnArial\fs32}Amethyst liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我从没想到我能伸展到那么远\N{\fnArial\fs32}I never thought I could stretch so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我感觉我貌似直接贯穿了某个星球！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I think I kind of phased through a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，史小子\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, yo, Ste-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:33.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你听到石榴说的话了\N{\fnArial\fs32}You heard Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们完全没事，哥们\N{\fnArial\fs32}We're totally fine, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我-我太心急了，我-\N{\fnArial\fs32}I-I was pushing so hard,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:41.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我只是非常想见到我爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs32}I just wanted to get Dad back so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我-我几乎搞砸了整个任务\N{\fnArial\fs32}I-I almost wrecked the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这都是我的错\N{\fnArial\fs32}This whole thing is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，不是你绑架的格雷格\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, you didn't kidnap Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是蓝钻石做的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Blue Diamond did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:54.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}喔，你们看到了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Whoa. Do you guys see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你所做的带我们到了动物园\N{\fnArial\fs32}What you did got us to the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:06.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而且只是提前了70人类年而已\N{\fnArial\fs32}And only 70 human years ahead of schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我很快会见到你的，爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'll see you really soon, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我希望\N{\fnArial\fs32}I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,
